title: Breaking Bad - Season Three (MP4)
description:
This is the third season of breaking bad converted to MP4 for the purposes of watching on my Vita. After spending an hour or more converting each one, it seemed someone else may appreciate me saving them the time should they have a preference or need for MP4 format.

The file size is small, but the show looks great on the Vita. How it may look on a larger screen someone else would have to tell you (if my computer ran well enough to run it,I would not have bothered converting it), but I would imagine it more than watchable.

There are no sub titles. None of my previous uploaded episodes did either, but this is the first one there has been enough spanish to matter. There isn't a whole lot, but enough I felt the need to read the subtitles for a few scenes at http://breakingbad.wikia.com/wiki/

Expect the rest of the seasons to follow.
